{"tid":328943,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去日本旅行去到中曬毒","createTime":"2017-07-20T03:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T14:39:32.000Z","uid":60219,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9b9fe28afea98e501ec1e260474d8dbc9e4679","tid":328943,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"之前去四國，舊年去關西同北九州，今年去完南九州，嚟緊八月又再去北九州去埋上次冇去到嘅長崎<br />\n太鍾意係日本果種旅遊模式，尤其自己仲係個學生哥budget有限，每次買UO機票住東橫inn偶然一晚住溫泉旅館，竹蔗價錢換嚟燒鵝味道，返香港隔一排見UO有優惠就又忍唔住手買<br />\n神奇嘅係去咁多次都唔會悶，點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42374251b569981a3058f92f9e88089348ae18c","tid":328943,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bc74af295acf376641f2dff8b346740055254dd","tid":328943,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝防毒先去囉</blockquote><br />\n即刻搏咀"},{"pid":"0012f0c10246d0826906c7a69b54273b43ef05cb","tid":328943,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"食野好貴喎<br />\n邊有咁多次"},{"pid":"df03ce97d647793e40f70472b1f10ed9b02520eb","tid":328943,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"我都好鐘意日本<br />\n學生哥plan 緊第三次去日本<br />\n上兩次去左大路d 嘅osaka/tokyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲有咩地方好推介？<br />\n因為見有d 地方幾偏下自駕遊先好玩<br />\n但學生鬼有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fd9ee43599438faca8daac3c97aa7a1d6692bb","tid":328943,"uid":129186,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"狗國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840c20643b4aa5908aa6ed54fb4625895e54752e","tid":328943,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝防毒先去囉</blockquote><br />\n即刻搏咀</blockquote><br />\ngay"},{"pid":"35c113ab63200484040ae67ed5bb41836494ed5d","tid":328943,"uid":74192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好鐘意日本<br />\n學生哥plan 緊第三次去日本<br />\n上兩次去左大路d 嘅osaka/tokyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲有咩地方好推介？<br />\n因為見有d 地方幾偏下自駕遊先好玩<br />\n但學生鬼有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n福岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fe34496a91679c3952d277548eaf9e4117255d","tid":328943,"uid":50123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食野好貴喎<br />\n邊有咁多次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同香港比日本食野一d都唔貴"},{"pid":"872cda22ff5426bfc84161e069783795cc234266","tid":328943,"uid":79252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食野好貴喎<br />\n邊有咁多次</blockquote><br />\n其實唔貴，特別而家一碟牛河都要40-50蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdf43628b97d8e87acf2182cf53aa781f885bc3","tid":328943,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食野好貴喎<br />\n邊有咁多次</blockquote><br />\n其實唔貴，特別而家一碟牛河都要40-50蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想食平嘢，可以食便利店/牛丼<br />\n中價嘢，定食餐廳同拉麵舖大把選擇<br />\n貴少少食魚生或者燒肉都平過香港，宮崎牛好撚正，南九州青島魚生又新鮮又平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09997db9241143b64895e6f495b9ffe40320156","tid":328943,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都好鐘意日本<br />\n學生哥plan 緊第三次去日本<br />\n上兩次去左大路d 嘅osaka/tokyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲有咩地方好推介？<br />\n因為見有d 地方幾偏下自駕遊先好玩<br />\n但學生鬼有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n福岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住今年學車，以後就可以自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇車嘅可以上JR個網睇下佢去邊d站，去日本唔揸車就一定要靠JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1855382dcc2c0778890346c0e686cd71f8300efa","tid":328943,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好鐘意日本<br />\n學生哥plan 緊第三次去日本<br />\n上兩次去左大路d 嘅osaka/tokyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲有咩地方好推介？<br />\n因為見有d 地方幾偏下自駕遊先好玩<br />\n但學生鬼有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70c3fc3153ae5bed7d16d9743d8564b4317d415","tid":328943,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都好鐘意日本<br />\n學生哥plan 緊第三次去日本<br />\n上兩次去左大路d 嘅osaka/tokyo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲有咩地方好推介？<br />\n因為見有d 地方幾偏下自駕遊先好玩<br />\n但學生鬼有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n福岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住今年學車，以後就可以自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇車嘅可以上JR個網睇下佢去邊d站，去日本唔揸車就一定要靠JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定要1take pass喎<br />\n唔係個國際執照要等到天荒地老先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4525702d6ce1484f2568dfe795fc73bfdadaaeab","tid":328943,"uid":88653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:39:32.0